### 2. `style.css`
```css
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background: #f0fdf4;
  color: #1b4332;
  text-align: center;
}

header {
  background: #2d6a4f;
  color: white;
  padding: 20px;
}

